rows.label: qst202719_0010
rows.name: Mimumu!

rows.label: qst202719_0020
rows.name: Mom...

rows.label: qst202719_0030
rows.name: Go on now. It's okay.

rows.label: qst202719_0040
rows.name:
Mom...
Mimumu sorry!

rows.label: qst202719_0050
rows.name: Sorry for make Mom worry!

rows.label: qst202719_0060
rows.name:
There, there...
Mom just glad you okay.

rows.label: qst202719_0070
rows.name: Mimumu not hurt anywhere?

rows.label: qst202719_0080
rows.name:
No, Mimumu healthy as Armu!
Thanks to Mei-san and others!

rows.label: qst202719_0090
rows.name:
Ah, that good...
That really good!

rows.label: qst202719_0100
rows.name:
Mom...
Mimumu was wrong.

rows.label: qst202719_0110
rows.name:
Mimumu blame problems on others,
run away when should have stayed...

rows.label: qst202719_0120
rows.name:
Mimumu should have just
talk with Mom...!

rows.label: qst202719_0130
rows.name: It not entirely fault of Mimumu...

rows.label: qst202719_0140
rows.name:
Mom also could have
listen to what Mimumu say more carefully.

rows.label: qst202719_0150
rows.name: ...This lesson, I learn from friend here.

rows.label: qst202719_0160
rows.name: Hm...

rows.label: qst202719_0170
rows.name: Hmm...being a parent looks great, eh?

rows.label: qst202719_0180
rows.name: I guess...

rows.label: qst202719_0190
rows.name:
Everyone in this world has ties,
even if it's just to one person...

rows.label: qst202719_0200
rows.name: Caring for that person is a good thing...

rows.label: qst202719_0210
rows.name: Just like with me and my Driver.
